{"tid":1842572,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"知唔知點解大家要一齊同醫護罷工","createTime":"2020-01-25T18:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T20:02:01.000Z","uid":84267,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ac312a9154d4ca8d302eb07121f71badc5fb5644","tid":1842572,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:30:27.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n我地普通工罷黎係無撚用<br />\n搞左幾次罷工都無咩效果<br />\n我地普通工亦無醫護既bargaining power<br />\n<br />\n<strong>醫護, 始終係唯一有籌碼嗰個</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但如果你以為只需要醫護自己罷工就得, 就大錯特錯</span><br />\n<br />\n而家醫護罷工除左怕被清算, 另外最大阻力就係黎自社會既道德壓力<br />\n<br />\n平時無事醫護本身已經壓力爆煲, 而家應付肺炎之餘, 罷工/反罷工既矛頭亦指向醫護, 加上社會上既道德責任, 醫護既精神壓力係不可想象<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">所以大家要同醫護一齊罷工</span></span><br />\n<strong>一齊罷</strong>, 係可以一齊負擔同減輕醫護既道德責任. 大家係共同體, 被政府道德綁架既話就一齊孭<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一齊罷</strong>, 對醫護黎講, 喺精神上已經差好遠<br />\n絕對有利醫護手足下決心做正確既決定<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>我已準備同醫護一齊罷工</ins></span>"},{"pid":"d023f04d639a3b4c74efa91ecaba7477b2d7fbb9","tid":1842572,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:32:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a5fd71a7d81d581e2bdbbb317dda46f7af926b2","tid":1842572,"uid":38563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:32:34.000Z","msg":"完全明白哩個道理<br />\n一定會一齊罷"},{"pid":"abdb229cbd118b1a4f61b90a1d998ccde9dbec9d","tid":1842572,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:32:50.000Z","msg":"點解淨係叫醫護罷工？明明封關關乎全香港人生命保障。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1841737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1841737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6fca0390d0408f84ffc622fc37906fccec183bf4","tid":1842572,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:33:00.000Z","msg":"保命要緊"},{"pid":"7821dd33fffc6d272c45ed732db6455b18fcda5d","tid":1842572,"uid":136916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:33:14.000Z","msg":"不要說「我支持醫護罷工。」<br />\n試著說「我準備好同醫護一齊罷。」"},{"pid":"15dd6d09a76a61393c56db9f97a51c9f0cfe91a4","tid":1842572,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:33:26.000Z","msg":"入去推一推<br />\n<br />\n請不要再說：「我支持醫護罷工。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1842379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1842379</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"06d334f4c2a9ee56af08870cde5b0aa420053007","tid":1842572,"uid":48452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:36:18.000Z","msg":"咪又係借醫護人員過橋達到政治目的<br />\n懶係包裝到齊上齊落噉"},{"pid":"f41d6d0c15c8534913c1b4c5f37c126e80d74079","tid":1842572,"uid":84267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:37:41.000Z","msg":"醫護係今次罷工既主角<br />\n但絕對需要我地班普通工一齊罷工<br />\n社會既道德責任我地一齊分擔"},{"pid":"98e40832b681a7dc3424064f0b26fcd0663e2bfe","tid":1842572,"uid":84267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"06d334f4c2a9ee56af08870cde5b0aa420053007","tid":1842572,"uid":48452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:36:18.000Z","msg":"咪又係借醫護人員過橋達到政治目的<br />\n懶係包裝到齊上齊落噉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:38:40.000Z","msg":"政你老母治目的<br />\n而家要封關呀, 講到唔關你事咁撚樣"},{"pid":"39ef558ed4c59ce67150917d291479dbd2e44e20","tid":1842572,"uid":48452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98e40832b681a7dc3424064f0b26fcd0663e2bfe","tid":1842572,"uid":84267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"06d334f4c2a9ee56af08870cde5b0aa420053007","tid":1842572,"uid":48452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:36:18.000Z","msg":"咪又係借醫護人員過橋達到政治目的<br />\n懶係包裝到齊上齊落噉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:38:40.000Z","msg":"政你老母治目的<br />\n而家要封關呀, 講到唔關你事咁撚樣"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:41:04.000Z","msg":"你哋熱愛香港係你哋嘅事<br />\n怨恨香港嘅我無需要負喱種責任"},{"pid":"f61d3db68c15f838f4f8e02d3d7c04c74bf86802","tid":1842572,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,